-- Austria’s Fekter Says Greece Needs to Speed Up Privatizations
-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 2012-06-19T09:13:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-19/austria-s-fekter-says-greece-needs-to-speed-up-privatizations.html
Austrian Finance Minister Maria Fekter said  Greece  needed to increase the speed in which its
sells state assets.  “We’ve always criticized that nothing has happened
regarding privatizations,” Fekter told reporters in Vienna
today. “More privatizations would create more dynamic and
competition, foreign investors would come to the country -- this
needs to be speeded up.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Zoe Schneeweiss at 
 zschneeweiss@bloomberg.net  